@* Shared view for including jQuery validation scripts.
   This view can be included in other views to enable client-side validation. *@

@* Script for jQuery Validation plugin.
   This plugin provides a way to perform validation on form fields and is highly customizable.
   It's used here to validate forms on the client side, improving user experience by providing immediate feedback on input. *@
<script src="~/lib/jquery-validation/dist/jquery.validate.min.js"></script>

@* Script for jQuery Validation Unobtrusive plugin.
   This plugin adds to jQuery Validation by enabling unobtrusive validation in ASP.NET.
   It uses data attributes instead of inline JavaScript, making the HTML cleaner and decoupling validation logic from HTML markup. *@
<script src="~/lib/jquery-validation-unobtrusive/jquery.validate.unobtrusive.min.js"></script>
